<p>This first Premium episode of the year sees Dave and John dig in right out of the gate, answering questions about Lion&rsquo;s Finder displays, managing energy saver settings automatically, three different questions about the Time Capsule and tons (and tons!) of Cool Stuff Found. All for you, Premium listener. What? You&rsquo;re not yet a Premium listener? Well, sign up today and change that. Just US$25 for 6 months of extra episodes and full archives, all while supporting your two favorite geeks!</p>
